%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 01c2cf2a4b2c62142a7668242814b230, type: 3}
  m_Name: TextConfig.Dialogs
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  category: Dialogs
  textDataList:
  - id: node_0001_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Wow, so this is the legendary Star Academy. Starting today, this is
        where I\u2019m going to shine."
    - language: 1
      text: "Wow, \u0111\xE2y ch\xEDnh l\xE0 H\u1ECDc Vi\u1EC7n Ng\xF4i Sao trong
        truy\u1EC1n thuy\u1EBFt sao. T\u1EEB ng\xE0y h\xF4m nay \u0111\xE2y s\u1EBD
        l\xE0 n\u01A1i m\xECnh \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\u1ECFa s\xE1ng."
  - id: node_0001_0003
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Hey, I heard that guy is the Headmaster's son, right?
    - language: 1
      text: "\xCA, nghe n\xF3i th\u1EB1ng kia l\xE0 con l\xE3o hi\u1EC7u tr\u01B0\u1EDFng
        ph\u1EA3i kh\xF4ng."
  - id: node_0001_0004
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Yeah, that's him. Just another privileged daddy's boy. (Sighs) I highly
        doubt he can actually do anything useful.
    - language: 1
      text: "\u1EEA, l\xE0 n\xF3 \u0111\xF3, l\u1EA1i th\xEAm m\u1ED9t th\u1EB1ng
        con \xF4ng ch\xE1u cha. Haizz, kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt c\xF3 l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
        tr\xF2 tr\u1ED1ng g\xEC kh\xF4ng n\u1EEFa."
  - id: node_0001_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Definitely not. These rich kids just coast by on their family connections.
    - language: 1
      text: "Ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn l\xE0 kh\xF4ng r\u1ED3i, m\u1EA5y th\u1EB1ng c\xF3
        ti\u1EC1n m\xE0, to\xE0n d\u1EF1a v\xE0o quy\u1EC1n th\u1EBF."
  - id: node_0001_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: (Thinking back to last night's conversation...) ---
    - language: 1
      text: "(H\u1ED3i t\u01B0\u1EDFng l\u1EA1i cu\u1ED9c tr\xF2 chuy\u1EC7n t\u1ED1i
        h\xF4m qua...) ---"
  - id: node_0001_0008
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: In the next few days, I will secure a position for you at the academy,
        and give you the best spirit beasts.
    - language: 1
      text: "M\u1EA5y h\xF4m n\u1EEFa, ta s\u1EBD s\u1EAFp \u0111\u1EB7t cho con
        m\u1ED9t v\u1ECB tr\xED t\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n, cho con nh\u1EEFng linh
        th\xFA gi\u1ECFi nh\u1EA5t."
  - id: node_0001_0009
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: All you have to do is perform well and climb the ranks.
    - language: 1
      text: "Vi\u1EC7c con c\u1EA7n l\xE0m ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n th\u1EADt
        t\u1ED1t \u0111\u1EC3 th\u0103ng ti\u1EBFn th\xF4i."
  - id: node_0001_0010
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: I don't need all that. I appreciate you helping me become a coach at
        the academy.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy, con c\u1EA3m \u01A1n b\u1ED1
        \u0111\xE3 gi\xFAp con \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n
        vi\xEAn t\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n"
  - id: node_0001_0011
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: But as for the rest... I'm going to have to decline.
    - language: 1
      text: "Nh\u01B0ng nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u c\xF2n l\u1EA1i \u2026 con xin
        ph\xE9p t\u1EEB ch\u1ED1i."
  - id: node_0001_0012
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: You are my son. Everything has been arranged, do not try to defy me.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con l\xE0 con trai c\u1EE7a ta, t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 m\u1ECDi th\u1EE9 ta
        \u0111\xE3 chu\u1EA9n b\u1ECB r\u1ED3i, \u0111\u1EEBng c\u1ED1 c\xE3i l\u1EDDi
        ta."
  - id: node_0001_0013
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: But like I said, I work by my own principles. I refuse to leave any student
        behind, and I don't want to just be known as your son.
    - language: 1
      text: "Nh\u01B0ng con c\u0169ng \u0111\xE3 n\xF3i r\u1ED3i, con l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c
        theo t\xF4n ch\u1EC9 c\u1EE7a m\xECnh, con kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n b\u1ECF b\u1EA5t
        c\u1EE9 h\u1ECDc vi\xEAn n\xE0o \u1EDF l\u1EA1i c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 kh\xF4ng
        mu\u1ED1n ph\u1EA3i mang c\xE1i danh con c\u1EE7a cha."
  - id: node_0001_0014
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: That much is obvious. Eventually, you will understand what I mean...
    - language: 1
      text: "V\u1ED1n d\u0129 \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0111\xF3 l\xE0 hi\u1EC3n nhi\xEAn,
        r\u1ED3i con s\u1EBD hi\u1EC3u nh\u1EEFng g\xEC ta n\xF3i\u2026"
  - id: node_0002_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: 'Oh, not bad at all. Congrats on making it to the finals.

'
    - language: 1
      text: "Oh, c\u0169ng kh\xE1 \u0111\u1EA5y nh\u1EC9, ch\xFAc m\u1EEBng c\u1EADu
        \u0111\xE3 l\u1ECDt v\xE0o tr\u1EADn chung k\u1EBFt."
  - id: node_0002_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Looks like I underestimated you. But don't kid yourself into thinking
        you actually have what it takes to beat me.
    - language: 1
      text: "C\xF3 v\u1EBB t\xF4i \u0111\xE3 \u0111\xE1nh gi\xE1 th\u1EA5p c\u1EADu,
        nh\u01B0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1EEBng ngh\u0129 r\u1EB1ng m\xECnh \u0111\u1EE7
        kh\u1EA3 n\u0103ng \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EA1i t\xF4i."
  - id: node_0002_0003
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Don't get too cocky. People who talk big usually fall the hardest. We'll
        see about that...
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\u1EEBng qu\xE1 t\u1EF1 tin, n\xF3i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc th\u01B0\u1EDDng
        b\u01B0\u1EDBc kh\xF4ng qua \u0111\xE2u, \u0111\u1EC3 xem..."
  - id: node_0003_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Still not calling it quits, Seiras? That\u2019s your 10,000th punch
        today already."
    - language: 1
      text: "V\u1EABn ch\u01B0a ch\u1ECBu d\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i sao, Seiras? \u0110\xE3
        l\xE0 c\xFA \u0111\u1EA5m th\u1EE9 10,000 trong ng\xE0y h\xF4m nay r\u1ED3i
        \u0111\u1EA5y."
  - id: node_0003_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "I can't stop... For someone like me, who can\u2019t even leave a scratch
        on an opponent, what else is there to do but persist?"
    - language: 1
      text: "T\xF4i kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 d\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i... M\u1ED9t k\u1EBB kh\xF4ng
        th\u1EC3 g\xE2y ra d\xF9 ch\u1EC9 m\u1ED9t v\u1EBFt x\u01B0\u1EDBc cho \u0111\u1ED1i
        th\u1EE7 nh\u01B0 t\xF4i, ngo\xE0i vi\u1EC7c ki\xEAn tr\xEC ra th\xEC c\xF2n
        l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c g\xEC n\u1EEFa?\r\n"
  - id: node_0003_0003
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "But look, that sandbag isn\u2019t torn, yet you haven\u2019t collapsed
        either. In this entire academy, is there anyone else with the stamina to
        stay standing after 10,000 consecutive punches?"
    - language: 1
      text: "Nh\u01B0ng nh\xECn xem, c\xE1i bao c\xE1t \u0111\xF3 kh\xF4ng h\u1EC1
        r\xE1ch, nh\u01B0ng c\u1EADu c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng h\u1EC1 ng\xE3 xu\u1ED1ng.
        C\u1EA3 h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n n\xE0y,\r\n c\xF3 ai \u0111\u1EE7 s\u1EE9c tr\u1EE5
        v\u1EEFng sau 10,000 c\xFA \u0111\u1EA5m li\xEAn t\u1EE5c nh\u01B0 c\u1EADu
        kh\xF4ng?"
  - id: node_0003_0004
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: They call me the 'disgrace'. A warrior without explosive power is nothing
        more than a walking target.
    - language: 1
      text: "H\u1ECD g\u1ECDi t\xF4i l\xE0 'n\u1ED7i h\u1ED5 th\u1EB9n'. M\u1ED9t
        chi\u1EBFn binh m\xE0 kh\xF4ng c\xF3 s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh b\xF9ng n\u1ED5 th\xEC
        ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 t\u1EA5m bia \u0111\u1EE1 \u0111\u1EA1n di \u0111\u1ED9ng
        th\xF4i."
  - id: node_0003_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "They\u2019re wrong. Strength isn't just about taking an opponent down
        in one blow; it\u2019s about being able to fight on forever when everyone
        else is exhausted. You aren't an outcast\u2014you are an eternal shield."
    - language: 1
      text: "H\u1ECD sai r\u1ED3i. S\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 n\u1EB1m
        \u1EDF vi\u1EC7c h\u1EA1 g\u1EE5c \u0111\u1ED1i ph\u01B0\u01A1ng trong m\u1ED9t
        \u0111\xF2n, m\xE0 l\xE0 vi\u1EC7c c\u1EADu c\xF3 th\u1EC3 chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u
        m\xE3i m\xE3i khi t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 \u0111\xE3 ki\u1EC7t s\u1EE9c. C\u1EADu
        kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i k\u1EBB b\u1ECB ru\u1ED3ng b\u1ECF, c\u1EADu l\xE0 l\xE1
        ch\u1EAFn b\u1EA5t di\u1EC7t."
  - id: node_0003_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Fight forever? You mean... this 'weakness' of mine could actually be
        a weapon?
    - language: 1
      text: "Chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u m\xE3i m\xE3i sao? \xDD anh l\xE0... s\u1EF1
        'b\u1EA5t l\u1EF1c' n\xE0y c\u1EE7a t\xF4i th\u1EF1c s\u1EF1 c\xF3 th\u1EC3
        tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh v\u0169 kh\xED?"
  - id: node_0003_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Exactly. When every formation crumbles, the last one standing is the
        one who leads. I\u2019ll stay right here until you finish your next punch."
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\xFAng v\u1EADy. Khi m\u1ECDi \u0111\u1ED9i h\xECnh tan r\xE3,
        k\u1EBB cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng c\xF2n \u0111\u1EE9ng v\u1EEFng ch\xEDnh l\xE0
        ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\u1EABn d\u1EAFt. T\xF4i s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EE9ng \u0111\xE2y
        cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi c\u1EADu ho\xE0n th\xE0nh c\xFA \u0111\u1EA5m ti\u1EBFp
        theo."
  - id: node_0003_0008
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Alright... Then for this 10,001st punch, I won\u2019t be hitting the
        sandbag. I\u2019m striking at my own limits!"
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\u01B0\u1EE3c... V\u1EADy th\xEC c\xFA \u0111\u1EA5m th\u1EE9
        10,001 n\xE0y, t\xF4i s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng \u0111\u1EA5m v\xE0o bao c\xE1t n\u1EEFa.
        T\xF4i \u0111\u1EA5m v\xE0o ch\xEDnh gi\u1EDBi h\u1EA1n c\u1EE7a m\xECnh!"
  - id: node_0004_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Look at this moron, he can't even see the exit right in front of him.
        Truly just a slab of meat meant to be a human shield!
    - language: 1
      text: "Nh\xECn k\xECa, g\xE3 \u0111\u1EA7n n\xE0y th\u1EADm ch\xED c\xF2n kh\xF4ng
        bi\u1EBFt l\u1ED1i tho\xE1t ngay tr\u01B0\u1EDBc m\u1EAFt. \u0110\xFAng l\xE0
        m\u1ED9t t\u1EA3ng th\u1ECBt ch\u1EC9 \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m bia \u0111\u1EE1
        \u0111\u1EA1n!"
  - id: node_0004_0003
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Stop it. This cheap game is over.
    - language: 1
      text: "D\u1EEBng tay l\u1EA1i. Tr\xF2 ch\u01A1i r\u1EBB ti\u1EC1n n\xE0y k\u1EBFt
        th\xFAc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c r\u1ED3i."
  - id: node_0004_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: 'I... I think. I think i can''t, I tried to find the patterns... but
        my head hurts so much. I really am just a fool, aren''t I?"

'
    - language: 1
      text: "T\xF4i... t\xF4i ngh\u0129 l\xE0 t\xF4i kh\xF4ng l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c.
        T\xF4i \u0111\xE3 c\u1ED1 t\xECm ra quy lu\u1EADt c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng... nh\u01B0ng
        \u0111\u1EA7u t\xF4i \u0111au qu\xE1. T\xF4i th\u1EADt s\u1EF1 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t
        k\u1EBB ng\u1ED1c ph\u1EA3i kh\xF4ng?"
  - id: node_0004_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "You\u2019re wrong, Tauroused. Your head hurts because you\u2019re trying
        to use your weakest weapon: 'calculation.' Listen to me\u2014from this moment
        on, stop thinking entirely.\r\n"
    - language: 1
      text: "Sai r\u1ED3i, Tauroused. C\u1EADu \u0111au \u0111\u1EA7u v\xEC anh \u0111ang
        c\u1ED1 d\xF9ng th\u1EE9 v\u0169 kh\xED y\u1EBFu nh\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a m\xECnh
        l\xE0 's\u1EF1 t\xEDnh to\xE1n'. H\xE3y nghe t\xF4i, t\u1EEB gi\u1EDD ph\xFAt
        n\xE0y... \u0111\u1EEBng suy ngh\u0129 g\xEC n\u1EEFa c\u1EA3."
  - id: node_0004_0008
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: 'Tactics are for the weak. For you, an illusion only exists if you acknowledge
        it. Let your instincts lead. Close your eyes and feel the ground beneath
        your feet. When you stop thinking, nothing can deceive you.

'
    - language: 1
      text: "Chi\u1EBFn thu\u1EADt l\xE0 d\xE0nh cho k\u1EBB y\u1EBFu. V\u1EDBi c\u1EADu,
        \u1EA3o \u1EA3nh ch\u1EC9 t\u1ED3n t\u1EA1i khi anh th\u1EEBa nh\u1EADn n\xF3.
        H\xE3y \u0111\u1EC3 b\u1EA3n n\u0103ng d\u1EABn d\u1EAFt, nh\u1EAFm m\u1EAFt
        l\u1EA1i v\xE0 c\u1EA3m nh\u1EADn m\u1EB7t \u0111\u1EA5t d\u01B0\u1EDBi ch\xE2n.
        Khi c\u1EADu kh\xF4ng ngh\u0129, kh\xF4ng c\xF3 g\xEC c\xF3 th\u1EC3 l\u1EEBa
        \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\u1EADu.\"\r\n"
  - id: node_0004_0009
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Don't think... just feel... I see it now. These rays of light... they
        carry no weight at all.
    - language: 1
      text: "Kh\xF4ng ngh\u0129... ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA3m nh\u1EADn... T\xF4i th\u1EA5y
        r\u1ED3i. Nh\u1EEFng lu\u1ED3ng s\xE1ng n\xE0y... ch\xFAng ch\u1EB3ng c\xF3
        tr\u1ECDng l\u01B0\u1EE3ng g\xEC c\u1EA3."
  - id: node_0005_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Another all-nighter with those numbers, Sakura? You\u2019ve recorded
        the trajectories of every single student in the academy."
    - language: 1
      text: "L\u1EA1i m\u1ED9t \u0111\xEAm tr\u1EAFng v\u1EDBi nh\u1EEFng con s\u1ED1
        sao, Sakura? Em \u0111\xE3 ghi ch\xE9p l\u1EA1i qu\u1EF9 \u0111\u1EA1o c\u1EE7a
        t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 h\u1ECDc vi\xEAn trong h\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n r\u1ED3i \u0111\u1EA5y."
  - id: node_0005_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "I have to... because I\u2019m too slow. If I don't pre-calculate their
        every move, I can't even last three seconds in the ring. I\u2019m a failure
        of a Virgo..."
    - language: 1
      text: "Em ph\u1EA3i l\xE0m v\u1EADy... V\xEC em qu\xE1 ch\u1EADm. N\u1EBFu
        kh\xF4ng t\xEDnh to\xE1n tr\u01B0\u1EDBc t\u1EEBng b\u01B0\u1EDBc di chuy\u1EC3n
        c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD, em th\u1EADm ch\xED kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 \u0111\u1EE9ng v\u1EEFng
        qu\xE1 ba gi\xE2y tr\xEAn s\xE0n \u0111\u1EA5u. Em l\xE0 m\u1ED9t X\u1EED
        N\u1EEF th\u1EA5t b\u1EA1i...\r\n"
  - id: node_0005_0003
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "You\u2019re forcing yourself into a race that isn't yours. Why should
        a 'Lentus' try to outrun the wind?"
    - language: 1
      text: "Em \u0111ang c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng \xE9p m\xECnh v\xE0o m\u1ED9t cu\u1ED9c
        \u0111ua t\u1ED1c \u0111\u1ED9 kh\xF4ng d\xE0nh cho m\xECnh. T\u1EA1i sao
        m\u1ED9t 'b\xF4ng hoa ch\u1EADm ch\u1EA1p' l\u1EA1i ph\u1EA3i c\u1ED1 ch\u1EA1y
        \u0111ua v\u1EDBi nh\u1EEFng c\u01A1n gi\xF3?"
  - id: node_0005_0004
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Because if I don't run, I\u2019ll be left behind. Everyone says I\u2019m
        a burden. What good is a warrior who can\u2019t even dodge an attack?"
    - language: 1
      text: "V\xEC n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng ch\u1EA1y, em s\u1EBD b\u1ECB b\u1ECF l\u1EA1i
        ph\xEDa sau. M\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EC1u n\xF3i em l\xE0 g\xE1nh
        n\u1EB7ng. M\u1ED9t chi\u1EBFn binh kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 n\xE9 \u0111\xF2n th\xEC
        c\xF3 \xEDch g\xEC ch\u1EE9?"
  - id: node_0005_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: 'They see slowness, but I see the steadfastness of a mountain. Listen,
        Sakura: Why run, when you can make the world come to a halt before you?'
    - language: 1
      text: "H\u1ECD nh\xECn th\u1EA5y s\u1EF1 ch\u1EADm ch\u1EA1p, nh\u01B0ng t\xF4i
        th\u1EA5y s\u1EF1 ki\xEAn \u0111\u1ECBnh c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t ng\u1ECDn n\xFAi.
        Nghe n\xE0y Sakura: T\u1EA1i sao ph\u1EA3i ch\u1EA1y, khi em c\xF3 th\u1EC3
        khi\u1EBFn th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi ph\u1EA3i d\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc
        m\u1EB7t em?"
  - id: node_0005_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Make the world... stop? You mean instead of trying to catch up, I should
        force them into my rhythm?
    - language: 1
      text: "Khi\u1EBFn th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi... d\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i sao? \xDD th\u1EA7y
        l\xE0 thay v\xEC c\u1ED1 b\u1EAFt k\u1ECBp h\u1ECD, em n\xEAn khi\u1EBFn
        h\u1ECD ph\u1EA3i r\u01A1i v\xE0o nh\u1ECBp \u0111i\u1EC7u c\u1EE7a em?"
  - id: node_0005_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Exactly. Don't strive to be faster. Turn your stillness into a domain
        where anyone who enters must slow down to your will. That is the absolute
        perfection a Virgo should truly strive for.
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\xFAng v\u1EADy. \u0110\u1EEBng c\u1ED1 nhanh h\u01A1n. H\xE3y
        bi\u1EBFn s\u1EF1 t\u0129nh l\u1EB7ng c\u1EE7a em th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t v\xF9ng
        kh\xF4ng gian m\xE0 b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 ai b\u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0o c\u0169ng ph\u1EA3i
        ch\u1EADm l\u1EA1i theo \xFD em. \u0110\xF3 m\u1EDBi l\xE0 s\u1EF1 ho\xE0n
        h\u1EA3o tuy\u1EC7t \u0111\u1ED1i m\xE0 m\u1ED9t X\u1EED N\u1EEF n\xEAn h\u01B0\u1EDBng
        t\u1EDBi."
  - id: node_0004_0010
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Exactly. Now, stop looking for an exit. Become the exit. Charge straight
        ahead and crush everything in your path!
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\xFAng th\u1EBF. Gi\u1EDD th\xEC, \u0111\u1EEBng t\xECm l\u1ED1i
        tho\xE1t n\u1EEFa. H\xE3y bi\u1EBFn m\xECnh th\xE0nh l\u1ED1i tho\xE1t. Lao
        th\u1EB3ng v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa tr\u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0 nghi\u1EC1n n\xE1t m\u1ECDi
        th\u1EE9 c\u1EA3n \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng anh!"
  - id: node_0004_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Stop thinking? But the instructor said that without tactics, I\u2019m
        just a wild beast, easily led by the nose...\r\n"
    - language: 1
      text: "Ng\u1EEBng suy ngh\u0129? Nh\u01B0ng HLV n\xF3i n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng c\xF3
        chi\u1EBFn thu\u1EADt, t\xF4i ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t con th\xFA hoang d\u1EC5
        b\u1ECB d\u1EAFt m\u0169i..."
  - id: node_0006_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: That's pretty good, but guys like him can't really accomplish anything...
    - language: 1
      text: "Kh\xE1 \u0111\u1EA5y, nh\u01B0ng nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB nh\u01B0 c\u1EADu
        ta c\u0169ng ch\u1EA3 l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c g\xEC \u0111\xE2u..."
  - id: node_0007_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Looks like I was mistaken,he's pretty talented
    - language: 1
      text: "C\xF3 v\u1EBB m\xECnh \u0111\xE3 l\u1EA7m, c\u1EADu ta kh\xE1 t\xE0i
        n\u0103ng \u0111\u1EA5y."
  - id: node_0007_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Time to start viewing him as a real threat.
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\xE3 \u0111\u1EBFn l\xFAc c\u1EA7n xem c\u1EADu ta l\xE0 m\u1ED9t
        \u0111\u1ED1i th\u1EE7 ti\u1EC1m n\u0103ng r\u1ED3i...\r\n"
  - id: node_0008_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Let\u2019s give a thunderous round of applause for our new King \u2013
        Seiras, who has reached the pinnacle of glory with unshakable courage and
        will!"
    - language: 1
      text: "H\xE3y d\xE0nh m\u1ED9t tr\xE0ng ph\xE1o tay n\u1ED3ng nhi\u1EC7t nh\u1EA5t
        cho T\xE2n V\u01B0\u01A1ng c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng ta \u2013 Seiras, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
        \u0111\xE3 chinh ph\u1EE5c \u0111\u1EC9nh cao vinh quang b\u1EB1ng b\u1EA3n
        l\u0129nh v\xE0 \xFD ch\xED kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 lay chuy\u1EC3n!"
  - id: node_0008_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: The victory is yours, the glory is yours
    - language: 1
      text: "Chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng g\u1ECDi t\xEAn b\u1EA1n, vinh quang thu\u1ED9c
        v\u1EC1 b\u1EA1n"
  - id: node_0009_0002
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: The victory is yours, the glory is yours
    - language: 1
      text: "Chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng g\u1ECDi t\xEAn b\u1EA1n, vinh quang thu\u1ED9c
        v\u1EC1 b\u1EA1n"
