  - id: node_0011_0001
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "Let\u2019s give a thunderous round of applause for our new King \u2013
        Tari, who has reached the pinnacle of glory with unshakable courage and will!"
    - language: 1
      text: "H\xE3y d\xE0nh m\u1ED9t tr\xE0ng ph\xE1o tay n\u1ED3ng nhi\u1EC7t nh\u1EA5t
        cho T\xE2n V\u01B0\u01A1ng c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng ta \u2013 Tari , ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
        \u0111\xE3 chinh ph\u1EE5c \u0111\u1EC9nh cao vinh quang b\u1EB1ng b\u1EA3n
        l\u0129nh v\xE0 \xFD ch\xED kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 lay chuy\u1EC3n!"
  - id: node_0011_0004
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: 'Congratulations, my son. I was wrong to doubt your potential. Those
        spirit beasts are far from weak; it is true that in the right hands, anything
        can become the ultimate strength.

'
    - language: 1
      text: "Ch\xFAc m\u1EEBng con trai, ta \u0111\xE3 sai khi nghi ng\u1EDD v\u1EC1
        n\u0103ng l\u1EF1c c\u1EE7a con. Nh\u1EEFng linh th\xFA \u0111\xF3, ch\xFAng
        ho\xE0n to\xE0n kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB y\u1EBFu, \u0111\xFAng
        l\xE0 khi v\xE0o tay \u0111\xFAng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, m\u1ECDi th\u1EE9 s\u1EBD
        tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh m\u1EA1nh nh\u1EA5t."
