        tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh m\u1EA1nh nh\u1EA5t."
  - id: node_0008_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Thank you, Father. Thank you for acknowledging my efforts. It is my wish
        to continue helping those spirit beasts deemed 'worthless' or cast aside
        by everyone else.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con c\u1EA3m \u01A1n cha, c\u1EA3m \u01A1n v\xEC cha \u0111\xE3 c\xF4ng
        nh\u1EADn nh\u1EEFng g\xEC con \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m, con c\u0169ng mong r\u1EB1ng
        s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c gi\xFAp \u0111\u1EE1 nh\u1EEFng linh th\xFA m\xE0
        m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi cho l\xE0 \"b\u1ECF \u0111i\" m\xE0 kh\xF4ng ai
        c\u1EA7n n\u1EEFa"
  - id: node_0009_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Thank you, Father. Thank you for acknowledging my efforts. It is my wish
        to continue helping those spirit beasts deemed 'worthless' or cast aside
