    - language: 0
      text: Thank you, Father. Thank you for acknowledging my efforts. It is my wish
        to continue helping those spirit beasts deemed 'worthless' or cast aside
        by everyone else.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con c\u1EA3m \u01A1n cha, c\u1EA3m \u01A1n v\xEC cha \u0111\xE3 c\xF4ng
        nh\u1EADn nh\u1EEFng g\xEC con \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m, con c\u0169ng mong r\u1EB1ng
        s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c gi\xFAp \u0111\u1EE1 nh\u1EEFng linh th\xFA m\xE0
        m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi cho l\xE0 \"b\u1ECF \u0111i\" m\xE0 kh\xF4ng ai
        c\u1EA7n n\u1EEFa"
  - id: node_0008_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "I am proud of you\u2014not merely for this victory, but for the compassion
        you show to all living beings. Go forth and use your own two hands to redefine
        the meaning of strength for the entire world to see."
    - language: 1
      text: "Ta t\u1EF1 h\xE0o v\u1EC1 con, kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 v\xEC chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng
        n\xE0y, m\xE0 v\xEC tr\xE1i tim bao dung con d\xE0nh cho v\u1EA1n v\u1EADt;
        h\xE3y \u0111i v\xE0 d\xF9ng ch\xEDnh \u0111\xF4i tay \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EC3
        vi\u1EBFt l\u1EA1i \u0111\u1ECBnh ngh\u0129a v\u1EC1 s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh cho
        c\u1EA3 th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi n\xE0y th\u1EA5y."
  - id: node_0009_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "I am proud of you\u2014not merely for this victory, but for the compassion
        you show to all living beings. Go forth and use your own two hands to redefine
        the meaning of strength for the entire world to see."
    - language: 1
      text: "Ta t\u1EF1 h\xE0o v\u1EC1 con, kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 v\xEC chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng
        n\xE0y, m\xE0 v\xEC tr\xE1i tim bao dung con d\xE0nh cho v\u1EA1n v\u1EADt;
        h\xE3y \u0111i v\xE0 d\xF9ng ch\xEDnh \u0111\xF4i tay \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EC3
        vi\u1EBFt l\u1EA1i \u0111\u1ECBnh ngh\u0129a v\u1EC1 s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh cho
        c\u1EA3 th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi n\xE0y th\u1EA5y."
