    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "I am proud of you\u2014not merely for this victory, but for the compassion
        you show to all living beings. Go forth and use your own two hands to redefine
        the meaning of strength for the entire world to see."
    - language: 1
      text: "Ta t\u1EF1 h\xE0o v\u1EC1 con, kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 v\xEC chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng
        n\xE0y, m\xE0 v\xEC tr\xE1i tim bao dung con d\xE0nh cho v\u1EA1n v\u1EADt;
        h\xE3y \u0111i v\xE0 d\xF9ng ch\xEDnh \u0111\xF4i tay \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EC3
        vi\u1EBFt l\u1EA1i \u0111\u1ECBnh ngh\u0129a v\u1EC1 s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh cho
        c\u1EA3 th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi n\xE0y th\u1EA5y."
  - id: node_0008_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Yes, Father. I will prove that no spirit beast is truly useless; there
        are only souls that have yet to find understanding and a place where they
        truly belong.
    - language: 1
      text: "V\xE2ng th\u01B0a cha, con s\u1EBD ch\u1EE9ng minh r\u1EB1ng kh\xF4ng
        c\xF3 linh th\xFA n\xE0o l\xE0 v\xF4 d\u1EE5ng, ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 nh\u1EEFng
        t\xE2m h\u1ED3n ch\u01B0a t\xECm th\u1EA5y s\u1EF1 th\u1EA5u hi\u1EC3u v\xE0
        m\u1ED9t n\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 thu\u1ED9c v\u1EC1 m\xE0 th\xF4i."
  - id: node_0009_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Yes, Father. I will prove that no spirit beast is truly useless; there
        are only souls that have yet to find understanding and a place where they
        truly belong.
    - language: 1
      text: "V\xE2ng th\u01B0a cha, con s\u1EBD ch\u1EE9ng minh r\u1EB1ng kh\xF4ng
        c\xF3 linh th\xFA n\xE0o l\xE0 v\xF4 d\u1EE5ng, ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 nh\u1EEFng
        t\xE2m h\u1ED3n ch\u01B0a t\xECm th\u1EA5y s\u1EF1 th\u1EA5u hi\u1EC3u v\xE0
        m\u1ED9t n\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 thu\u1ED9c v\u1EC1 m\xE0 th\xF4i."
  - id: node_0010_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Yes, Father. I will prove that no spirit beast is truly useless; there
        are only souls that have yet to find understanding and a place where they
        truly belong.
    - language: 1
      text: "V\xE2ng th\u01B0a cha, con s\u1EBD ch\u1EE9ng minh r\u1EB1ng kh\xF4ng
        c\xF3 linh th\xFA n\xE0o l\xE0 v\xF4 d\u1EE5ng, ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 nh\u1EEFng
        t\xE2m h\u1ED3n ch\u01B0a t\xECm th\u1EA5y s\u1EF1 th\u1EA5u hi\u1EC3u v\xE0
        m\u1ED9t n\u01A1i \u0111\u1EC3 thu\u1ED9c v\u1EC1 m\xE0 th\xF4i."
  - id: node_0011_0004
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: I am not grieving the loss, Father. I have simply realized that whether
        I win or lose, this world only sees spirit beasts as tools for glory, and
        I no longer wish to be a part of that cycle.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con kh\xF4ng bu\u1ED3n v\xEC tr\u1EADn thua, th\u01B0a cha. Con ch\u1EC9
        nh\u1EADn ra r\u1EB1ng, d\xF9 con c\xF3 th\u1EAFng hay thua, th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi
        n\xE0y v\u1EABn ch\u1EC9 coi linh th\xFA l\xE0 c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 \u0111\u1EC3
        \u0111o\u1EA1t l\u1EA5y vinh quang, v\xE0 con kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n l\xE0 m\u1ED9t
        ph\u1EA7n c\u1EE7a gu\u1ED3ng quay \u0111\xF3 n\u1EEFa."
  - id: node_0011_0005
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: I am not grieving the loss, Father. I have simply realized that whether
        I win or lose, this world only sees spirit beasts as tools for glory, and
        I no longer wish to be a part of that cycle.
    - language: 1
      text: "Con kh\xF4ng bu\u1ED3n v\xEC tr\u1EADn thua, th\u01B0a cha. Con ch\u1EC9
        nh\u1EADn ra r\u1EB1ng, d\xF9 con c\xF3 th\u1EAFng hay thua, th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi
        n\xE0y v\u1EABn ch\u1EC9 coi linh th\xFA l\xE0 c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 \u0111\u1EC3
        \u0111o\u1EA1t l\u1EA5y vinh quang, v\xE0 con kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n l\xE0 m\u1ED9t
        ph\u1EA7n c\u1EE7a gu\u1ED3ng quay \u0111\xF3 n\u1EEFa."
  - id: node_0011_0006
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: The Academy can change if you stay! Do not throw away your future as
        a trainer just when I am finally ready to stand by you. You have the talent,
        and they need to see it.
    - language: 1
      text: "H\u1ECDc vi\u1EC7n s\u1EBD thay \u0111\u1ED5i n\u1EBFu c\xF3 con \u1EDF
        l\u1EA1i! \u0110\u1EEBng v\u1EE9t b\u1ECF t\u01B0\u01A1ng lai l\xE0m hu\u1EA5n
        luy\u1EC7n vi\xEAn ngay l\xFAc ta \u0111\xE3 s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng \u0111\u1EE9ng
        v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa con. Con c\xF3 t\xE0i n\u0103ng, v\xE0 h\u1ECD c\u1EA7n th\u1EA5y
        \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0111\xF3."
  - id: node_0011_0007
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: "I am done being a trainer, for I no longer wish to 'train' anyone. I
        will find a land where they can live freely\u2014where they are friends,
        not warriors who must bleed just to earn someone's validation."
    - language: 1
      text: "Con s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng l\xE0m hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n vi\xEAn n\u1EEFa, v\xEC
        con kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n 'hu\u1EA5n luy\u1EC7n' b\u1EA5t k\u1EF3 ai c\u1EA3.
        Con s\u1EBD \u0111i t\xECm m\u1ED9t v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t m\xE0 ch\xFAng
        c\xF3 th\u1EC3 s\u1ED1ng t\u1EF1 do, n\u01A1i ch\xFAng l\xE0 nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
        b\u1EA1n, kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i l\xE0 nh\u1EEFng chi\u1EBFn binh ph\u1EA3i \u0111\u1ED5
        m\xE1u \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\u1ED5i l\u1EA5y s\u1EF1 c\xF4ng nh\u1EADn."
